back to visit me.

270
00:14:27,625 --> 00:14:29,916
Wait a second,
do you mean...

271
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,875
Turns out your
instinct was right...

272
00:14:31,958 --> 00:14:33,833
She appeared at my
window last evening

273
