if something bad had happened?

280
00:14:53,375 --> 00:14:56,166
Well, obviously, if it
had I would have called...

281
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:58,625
but we just had a little
staring contest...

282
00:14:58,708 --> 00:15:00,208
so stop worrying.

283
00:15:03,208 --> 00:15:05,208
Then there's no way
it could be Kasai

284
00:15:07,541 --> 00:15:09,500
I mean, for her to
cast a such big curse,

285
00:15:09,583 --> 00:15:11,666
she'd have to have a lot
of that PK-whatever power,

286
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,458
wouldn't she?

287
00:15:12,541 --> 00:15:14,416
It's PK-LT...

288
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,666
But you are right, if she
wanted to be able to affect

289
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,166
so many people
with this curse,

290
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:21,291
she would need to have
quite a lot of that power.

291
00:15:21,375 --> 00:15:22,583
When we met her
the first time

292
00:15:22,666 --> 00:15:24,750
she wasn't even able
to bend that spoon...

293
00:15:24,833 --> 00:15:26,083
That's right...

294
00:15:26,166 --> 00:15:27,833
And spirits appeared
to all of the victims

295
00:15:27,916 --> 00:15:29,958
in every single incident

296
00:15:30,041 --> 00:15:32,208
The Kasai theory
definitively doesn't account

297
00:15:32,291 --> 00:15:33,916
for these apparitions.

298
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,458
Well, maybe she's
just off making

299
00:15:37,541 --> 00:15:39,083
effigy dolls or something.

300
00:15:39,166 --> 00:15:41,041
