00:15:45,708 --> 00:15:47,666
But whenever you use
straw effigy dolls

304
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:49,125
isn't it only supposed
to only hurt the person

305
00:15:49,208 --> 00:15:51,083
where the nail is driven in?

306
00:15:51,166 --> 00:15:53,583
She's right, and dolls
do not summon spirits.

307
00:15:53,666 --> 00:15:54,875
Course not...

308
00:15:54,958 --> 00:15:56,916
Moreover, they don't
possess the power

309
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,208
to have caused
repeated hauntings.

310
00:15:59,291 --> 00:16:00,916
-Lin!
-Yes...

311
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,833
it's possible
that's the answer.

312
00:16:03,916 --> 00:16:05,291
C'mon, fill us in.

313
00:16:05,375 --> 00:16:07,458
I can't believe I didn't
think of it sooner...

314
00:16:11,125 --> 00:16:12,791
Were dealing
with a zuzhou.

315
00:16:12,875 --> 00:16:14,416
A zuzhou?!

316
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:16,625
There's an extremely powerful
hex at work in this school

317
00:16:16,708 --> 00:16:18,416
to that's calling
down curses on people.

318
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,875
Are you serious?!

319
00:16:19,958 --> 00:16:21,416
Okay, but what's
the connection

320
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:23,708
between the zuzhou
and these spirits?

321
00:16:23,791 --> 00:16:26,833
This hex ,originally
derived from the Yin-yan Tao,

322
00:16:26,916 --> 00:16:28,958
is cast by driving a
nail into a hitogata,

323
00:16:29,041 --> 00:16:30,916
or straw effigy doll...

324
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,541
I'll explain this
so Mai can catch up.

325
00:16:33,625 --> 00:16:35,083
In the Yin-yan Tao

326
00:16:35,166 --> 00:16:36,541
there's a certain
method of cursing people

327
00:16:36,625 --> 00:16:39,000
referred to as enmi.

328
00:16:39,083 --> 00:16:41,083
It's a hex that uses
either a hitogata

329
00:16:41,166 --> 00:16:43,458
or a possession of
the one being cursed,

330
00:16:43,541 --> 00:16:45,500
and driving a nail into
the straw effigy doll

331
00:16:45,583 --> 00:16:47,666
is one of the enmi arts.

332
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:50,750
The doll's function is to simply
convey the level of hatred

333
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:52,458
of the person
driving the nail...

334
00:16:52,541 --> 00:16:55,125
the dolls themselves
can do no real harm.

335
00:16:55,208 --> 00:16:57,458
But when the hexer, the
one performing the curse,

336
00:16:57,541 --> 00:16:59,625
drives the nail
into the hitogata,

337
00:16:59,708 --> 00:17:03,250
they call upon gods or spirits
to deliver a deathcurse.

338
00:17:03,333 --> 00:17:04,333
Deathcurse?

339
00:17:04,416 --> 00:17:06,500
The gods or spirits
accept the task,

340
00:17:06,583 --> 00:17:09,500
and carry the curse to
the unlucky subject.

341
00:17:09,583 --> 00:17:10,833
In other words,

342
00:17:10,916 --> 00:17:12,375
the hexer actually contracts

343
00:17:12,458 --> 00:17:14,875
these gods, spirits
and even demons

344
00:17:14,958 --> 00:17:18,083
by performing the enmi arts.

345
00:17:18,166 --> 00:17:20,416
So you're saying that
the cursed desk...

346
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:23,041
the hand that
attacked Mr. oshino...

347
00:17:23,125 --> 00:17:25,916
And that woman that came
down from the ceiling...

348
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,250
Were all evil
spirits with curses?

349
00:17:28,333 --> 00:17:30,708
Someone has cast multiple
enmi spells against people

350
00:17:30,791 --> 00:17:32,041
at this school

351
00:17:32,125 --> 00:17:33,416
and evil spirits are
appearing to those

352
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:34,666
who have been cursed.

353
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:35,875
The spirits aren't
powerful enough

354
00:17:35,958 --> 00:17:38,000
to kill their targets
immediately

355
00:17:38,083 --> 00:17:40,041
so they torment and lead
them to their deaths.

356
00:17:40,125 --> 00:17:42,500
It's a very indirect
form of murder.

357
00:17:42,583 --> 00:17:44,625
And if these attacks were
to happen frequently,

358
00:17:44,708 --> 00:17:46,333
as they have at Yuasa...

359
00:17:46,416 --> 00:17:48,833
It would definitely have a
negative effect on those people

360
00:17:48,916 --> 00:17:50,666
who are easily influenced.

361
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:53,125
Yes... an extreme
example would be the girl

362
00:17:53,208 --> 00:17:55,000
who believed she was
possessed by a fox.

363
00:17:59,458 --> 00:18:01,541
This explains both the
incidents themselves

364
00:18:01,625 --> 00:18:05,125
and why the entire school was
thrown into such a panic.

365
00:18:05,208 --> 00:18:07,000
So who performed
the curses?

