00:18:14,416 --> 00:18:16,083
look her abilities
were rejected

372
00:18:16,166 --> 00:18:18,041
and in turn she was
made fun of and attacked

373
00:18:18,125 --> 00:18:19,791
in front of the
whole school, right?

374
00:18:19,875 --> 00:18:21,041
And even her teacher friend

